track.name: She Loves Me Not
comments: New stuff to me, I have yet another band to enjoy now.

@Killed-by-death. I like this sound better too but let's be honest. Nu metal, especialy this rap-metal styling was the "in" thing at the time so that's what they did. They were always going for the sales from the beginning. I don't care though. THis is a good song so I enjoy it for what it is.
I'm the jerk, life's not fair...
under rated band in my opinion

jrluk1: One of the last songs i listen to from them since they jumped on the sell out band wagon and turned into uber douches.. some of those recent pics are embarrassing compared to the early days.. *sigh* *strokes infest album* lol      //     sums it up pretty well
The only Papa Roach song I can play over and over again.
It's been a long time papa roach.
